'''''abonnen''''' (''pl. ebœnnin'') is a [[Sindarin]] word meaning:

# ''adj.'' Born later, born after
# ''n.'' Man, one born later than the elves, a human being

Derived from ''[[ab-]]'' + ''[[onnen]]'' "after-born".
